HOW TO RUN
──────────
Just double-click any .html file to open it in your browser.
No server, no internet, no installation needed.
 
Or in VS Code:
  1. Install the "Live Server" extension (optional, but nicer)
  2. Right-click the .html file → "Open with Live Server"
  OR simply press Ctrl+Shift+P → "Open in Default Browser"
  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
TASK 4 — Task3_ObjectDetection.html
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Tool: Object Detection & Tracking
Tech: Simulated YOLO detector + SORT tracker + Kalman Filter
      + IoU-based Hungarian association + canvas rendering
Features:
  • 7 scene presets (Street, Office, Park, Traffic, etc.)
  • SORT tracking algorithm with Kalman Filter prediction
  • DeepSORT-style trajectory trails
  • Bounding boxes with corner marks + confidence bars
  • Upload your own image for detection
  • Per-object tracking ID, confidence, coordinates
  • Real-time FPS counter, system log
  • Configurable confidence & IoU thresholds
  • Start / Pause / Stop / Clear controls